    <item>
      <title>Version 3.4.2</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <p><strong>Audio reliability fixes plus a friendlier, more informative menu.</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>All your outputs are now audible after routing.</strong> Your current volume level is carried across to every device AudioRouterNow routes to.</li>
          <li><strong>No more brief drop-outs when adding a third output.</strong> Adding another output on multi-output setups no longer cuts out the others.</li>
          <li><strong>The menu stays open while you set things up.</strong></li>
          <li><strong>The menu bar icon no longer cries wolf.</strong> It stays green when audio is still routing fine.</li>
          <li><strong>New: Help &#8594; Status Guide.</strong> A built-in colour legend for the menu bar icon states.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>No action required. Update normally.</p>
      ]]></description>
